### Armazenar o Token da resposta acima
@authToken = {{login.response.body.token}}


### List Users
GET {{url}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### User details
GET {{url}}/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create User
POST {{url}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

